description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 2 of 4 of the live May match up between Team Ice and The Pirates.
After the end of the first round The Pirates had an 18pt lead. Round two starts with the rookies battling it out. Mellanie Monroe faces off with Jessie Cox. Which team will get the first tag and start racking up the 2 on 1 points?
Ariel X steps up her game and dominates this round. The Pirates have nothing Ariel can't counter or attack into the ground. Ariel X dominating Dia and fingering her during one on one action is the difference in the round. Was it enough to take the lead into the locker room, going into the final round of wrestling?
title: ROUND TWO:
